snd-zg01-dkms (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Full-duplex audio support (playback and capture)
  * Game channel playback working perfectly
  * Voice channel capture working correctly
  * Fixed buffer size calculation bug (no more sample skipping)
  * Fixed kernel panic issues (bounds checking)
  * Optimized URB buffering (16 URBs = 64ms)
  * Support for xHCI controllers (localhost) and VM environments
  * Clean compilation without warnings

